{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script aims to improve video derush by constantly moving edit cursor at the end of time selecion while playing.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Move edit cursor to the end of time selection while playing\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script aimes to replace edit cursor at the end time selection while we are playing.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 I mainly use it to improve video derush as it let me keep playing and create regions and if I stop, it restart from the end of my newly created region (which match with time selection here).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 It runs in background (reaper.defer()) and acts as a toggle. So it constantly replace the cursor while playing.\par}
}

