{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script aims to rename item with folder name (if track is in folder) - track name - item position in the track\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 WARNING : it's a persistent script, continuously running in background.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 USER OPTIONS\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b {\f1 SHOW_PARENT_FOLDER}} If this option is set to 1 folder name will appear in item name. 0 to not show the folder name\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b {\f1 SHOW_TRACK_NAME}} If this option is set to 1 track name will appear in item name. 0 to not show the track name\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b {\f1 SHOW_ITEM_NBR}} If this option is set to 1 item number will appear in item name. 0 to not show the item number\par}
}

